transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Haan. 
Executive: Sir ho gaya uska wo solution jo aap keh rahe the wo contact number.
Customer: Haan ji.
Customer: Haan, bataiye.
Executive: Sir search kar liya aapne wo seller ka wo contact number.
Customer: Haan search kar liya wo contact number par chal raha hai wo bhej raha hai humko.
Executive: To aap ek kaam karna sir na aapko aage se koi bhi dikkat ho mera ye number save kar lo. Theek hai?
Customer: Theek.
Executive: Aap mujhe direct call kijiyega kisi bhi cheez ki requirement ho theek hai na?
Customer: Theek hai.
Executive: Haan ji to abhi aapko ye jo aapka concern raise hua tha iske liye sir mere liye feedback aayega aapko mail pe. Theek hai?
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: To uska revert back kar dijiyega aap sir.
Customer: Theek hai kar denge.
Executive: Haan ji theek hai.
Customer: Hello.
